{
  "stem": "25639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And once in a while, mother would wrap around-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] find something and wrap it around with some cloth, some kind of clothes, and weigh it down with a piece of stone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was-- there was gravel, sort of rough stone-like gravel all around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she would throw the-- this package across the electric wire fence into the twin lager, the twin camps, where they experimented on-- on-- where the-- these were girls and boys on whom they experimented on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Actually, I don't remember boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I only remember girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So maybe they kept the boys elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they really were very thin and emaciated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And mother wanted to help out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She did this a few times, and then she was caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was taken to the lager kommandant by the kapo this time, by the kapo.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And luckily-- luckily for my mother, the kapo liked her-- liked my mother-- and knew that there was a very young [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] daughter that works also under her command.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And but took my mother to the kapo and said that this woman threw a-- a package over to the twin lager, and she should be-- she should be reprimanded.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and he barked I'll decide what has to be done with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he was going to tell her how many lashes that she should get when she didn't permit him to say this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And instead she added, before he could say anything, this woman's young girl, is my very best worker, herr kommandant, and if I lose her, I'm going to lose her daughter too.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so he got the message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I suppose sometimes they listened to the kapos.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
